Package: bsvarPost
Type: Package
Title: Post-Estimation Tools for 'bsvars' and 'bsvarSIGNs'
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2026-03-07
Authors@R: person("David", "Zenz", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "office@davidzenz.com")
Author: David Zenz [aut, cre]
Maintainer: David Zenz <office@davidzenz.com>
Description: Companion post-estimation tools for Bayesian structural vector autoregressions fitted with the 'bsvars' and 'bsvarSIGNs' packages. It adds cumulative dynamic multipliers, tidy extraction helpers, model comparison utilities, and a 'ggplot2' plotting layer on top of existing posterior objects.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    bsvars,
    bsvarSIGNs,
    ggplot2,
    tibble,
    methods
Suggests:
    APRScenario,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    tinytest,
    tsibble
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
URL: https://github.com/DavidZenz/bsvarPost
